title: War of the Roses: I Know You Hate Peppers
description: Abigail think her boyfriend, Neil might be cheating because he's sick pretty often and when he gets sick, he doesn't allow her to come over.  Also, he recently ordered them a pizza and was so proud he remembered she doesn't like peppers, but Abigail is fine with eating peppers so she thinks he's seeing someone else who doesn't like peppers.
